rComments: McCarthy is such a kind lady. She is VERY fair and VERY clear in what she expects of us. No mid term, no textbook, all articles (Which are actually interesting). Go to class and listen, she drops hints about the final. MEMORIZE AND UNDERSTAND EACH ARTICLE FOR THE FINAL!!
teacherRatingTags: ['Lecture heavy', 'Get ready to read', 'Gives good feedback']

rComments: There is no midterm, but be prepared to memorize all the readings for the final and the questions she asks are very specific. Also, her feedback for presentations was not very consistent and clear. Following the rubric did not help and she can get very defensive and uptight about her grading. She does not care much about students.
